      ],
      "content": "Download the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Web and Business Database Migration Guidance Cookbook<ept id=\"p1\">](http://download.microsoft.com/download/3/C/9/3C9FF3D8-E702-4F5D-A38C-5EFA1DBA73E6/Azure_SQL_Database_Migration_Cookbook.pdf)</ept>."
    },
