      ],
      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">[AZURE.NOTE]</ph> <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Pricing tier recommendations<ept id=\"p1\">](sql-database-service-tier-advisor.md)</ept> for Web and Business databases are now available."
