    {
      "pos": [
        5314,
        5605
      ],
      "content": "For example, consider how long backups need to be retained, or if <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Standard or Active Geo-Replication<ept id=\"p1\">](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/azure/dn783447.aspx)</ept> features are needed, or the overall maximum database size needed, etc. These requirements determine your minimum service tier choice."
    },
    {
      "content": "The ‘Basic’ tier is primarily used for very small, low activity databases.",
      "pos": [
