    {
      "content": "Web and Business database resource consumption data is accessed through the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>sys.resource_stats<ept id=\"p1\">](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/azure/dn269979.aspx)</ept> view in the master database of the logical server where your current database is located.",
