    {
      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">[AZURE.NOTE]</ph> You can now use the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>sys.dm_db_resource_stats<ept id=\"p1\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/dn800981.aspx)</ept> view in Web and Business databases for a higher granularity view (every 15 seconds) of resource consumption data.",
